## Build & flash — ESP-IDF

```bash
idf.py set-target {{ idf_target }}
idf.py flash monitor
```

The first build downloads `espressif/esp-tflite-micro` via the IDF Component
Manager (see `main/idf_component.yml`).

## Build & flash — PlatformIO

```bash
pio run -t upload -t monitor
```

## Wiring in your real input

Replace `fill_input()` in `main/main.cc` with your sensor read + preprocessing.
The current implementation feeds zeros so you can verify latency and memory
before integrating.

## Files

- `main/model_data.cc` — the model flatbuffer as a 16-byte-aligned C array
- `main/main.cc` — interpreter setup, minimal op resolver, timed inference loop
- `main/idf_component.yml` — TFLM runtime dependency (managed component)
- `NOTICE` — licenses of bundled third-party runtime components
